Types of databases:
- Relational Database
  Mysql, Postgres, Mongo, Nosql etc.
  
Postgres favoured by open source community
  
SQL => Structured Query Language

Postgres cheat sheet: http://blog.jasonmeridth.com/posts/postgresql-command-line-cheat-sheet/

Should never interact directly with the data => Use an ORM.

Learn SELECT, UPDATE, DELETE, INSERT INTO, CREATE DATABASE SQL commands. => Learn SQL the hard way

Models directory => Database setup for a user, link, etc.
Models should always be singular => user.rb instead of users.rb

  
